{"tid":330282,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"你地呢排有冇啲好奇怪嘅電話打黎？","createTime":"2017-07-21T05:07:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-21T07:21:27.000Z","uid":89901,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"4a99455bd4a1e0553831f5490a95f8d29c3dbd7c","tid":330282,"uid":89901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:07:18.000Z","msg":"一星期收到2個電話都係老野打黎<br />\n<br />\n第一個就係阿伯黎<br />\n話咩bb呀 我好掛住你呀<br />\n我一聽打錯電話 cut佢線 同block咗佢<br />\n<br />\n咁一個打錯都正常嘅<br />\n<br />\n跟住今朝又有個阿姨打黎<br />\n呢個人就搵乜乜玲嘅<br />\n我身邊冇人有個玲字 咁我都係cut 線加block佢<br />\n<br />\n隔一陣佢就留言比我 但我唔敢聽 覺得好恐怖<br />\n<br />\n你地有冇人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/130642_5384471a5d4d3019ad6a631bfb051db5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F130642_5384471a5d4d3019ad6a631bfb051db5.jpg&h=40fd5a8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/130653_3abbfd38ed08fe8fe775436f59ada827.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F130653_3abbfd38ed08fe8fe775436f59ada827.jpg&h=a83dd119&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89cc1b1467b645df5d94f3d8be5adde765843e3e","tid":330282,"uid":48285,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:09:38.000Z","msg":"就快7月節，係咁㗎喇"},{"pid":"e7e945f048316e07c54d8778d5cbd53f2ea8aaff","tid":330282,"uid":89901,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就快7月節，係咁㗎喇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n認真呢 唔好嚇我好驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5ca97fa5ef7d151c1152e5775024266d72e47c","tid":330282,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:33:06.000Z","msg":"打錯啫"},{"pid":"dc7daf1e9e57a6b1521eec6d85b59e8f012f78fe","tid":330282,"uid":89901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:37:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>打錯啫</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n忍唔住叫同事陪我聽咗個留言<br />\n係打完唔記得收線嘅聲黎<br />\n都話打錯仲係咁打黎<br />\n<br />\n十年都冇人打錯過我電話 突然有所以都幾驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fa52f270fe98b60d695af9c64bdb89b98ca682","tid":330282,"uid":29781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:39:56.000Z","msg":"頭幾個number都同我一樣<br />\n嚇咗嚇"},{"pid":"53062ce4dd4042571f5a9afcbebf4a03899cd9f0","tid":330282,"uid":112489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:43:30.000Z","msg":"你個電話印左係一樓一門口"},{"pid":"d5fbfc9607540cfd96b660e8d0bffddce69c3a05","tid":330282,"uid":89901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭幾個number都同我一樣<br />\n嚇咗嚇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好再打黎 我唔會聽㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7eb14b6a0fa00e4b390681897e58d8120f5d8f1","tid":330282,"uid":89901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T05:50:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你個電話印左係一樓一門口</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔會掛 我冇得罪咩人喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1bb4a4f681639847f973b652285607814e7f38b","tid":330282,"uid":89901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T06:11:04.000Z","msg":"又黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係咪應該聽佢電話叫佢唔好再打黎<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/21/141057_2097b8a65552683499c64966d0e365cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F21%2F141057_2097b8a65552683499c64966d0e365cd.jpg&h=9d632c07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd152648cc0d5d8764a455a2282efc3f448482e3","tid":330282,"uid":109690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"